    "120695464": {
      "title": "Effective five-wave Hamiltonian for surface water waves",
      "abstract": "Abstract An effective five-wave Hamiltonian for one-dimensional water waves on the surface of an infinitely deep ideal fluid is presented. The diagrammatic technique is used. For some particular orientations of wave vectors the interaction matrix element is exactly zero, while for others it is given by remarkably simple formulas. This is another surprising result of water wave theory."
